Package: dmdprices
Title: Look Up Medicine Prices from the NHS dm+d
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Will", "Hardy", email = "w.hardy@bangor.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides the bundled NHS dm+d (Dictionary of Medicines and
    Devices) pricing dataset (Week 34 2025) and tools to query Drug Tariff
    and NHS Indicative Prices by medicine name. Also supports loading updated
    releases from the NHSBSA dmdDataLoader CSV output. Output columns mirror
    the NHS Drug Tariff Part VIIIA CSV format so that dm+d and Drug Tariff
    files can be used together directly. The dm+d data is Crown copyright,
    licensed under the Open Government Licence v3.0
    <https://www.nationalarchives.gov.uk/doc/open-government-licence/version/3/>.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
